  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111450/extras/9ebea0386a15bff3d0c8cf0e13c8ff0e.avif?t=1567163241\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br>==== ==== ABOUT ==== ==== <br>21世纪，电竞观众已达数十亿——<br>电竞项目加入奥运会，职业电竞选手万众瞩目。<br>在某电竞大国，每年都会举办高校电竞联赛，天才选手一较高下！<br>突然有一天，大小姐杨海遥站在我面前说——<br> “ 我给你钱，你给我一个电竞战队！ ” <br><br>==== ==== STORY ==== ====<br>大小姐杨海遥挥舞钞票，将我拉入电子竞技大业。<br>我到底是战队经理人，还是负责点外卖的？<br>人手不足，还得把青梅竹马沈雨涵也拉进战队？<br>然而我可爱的青梅竹马，竟然也有自己的秘密？<br>宿敌出现，我们该如何一起面对？<br>同时被两个心爱女孩的告白，我又该如何选择？<br>——“ 青羽 ”战队的传奇故事，就此开始！<br><br>==== ====  Character  ==== ====<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111450/extras/e8fa2aaaa6b0b5e55c384c664fe6e399.avif?t=1567163241\" width=504 height=720 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111450/extras/68228879b8448d13c43139752fd4aac3.avif?t=1567163241\" width=504 height=772 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111450/extras/1ab02a2ebc5192bea41a551d32c8a5a8.avif?t=1567163241\" width=504 height=638 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111450/extras/42f85c5a93f2fd9793d76cad8c8cd6fe.avif?t=1567163241\" width=504 height=668 /></span><br><br>==== ==== STAFF  ==== ====<br>企划：Youth Feather Center<br>监督：白歌<br>剧本：雨浮凉<br>配音：<br>—杨海遥 —— 真遥<br>—沈雨涵 —— 月夜桥<br>—安娜 —— 知秋酱<br>—杨溪溪 —— 写川<br>原画：SOLA<br>制作：龍之咲 HD<br>背景：背景専門店みにくる<br>音乐：Terry Chandler<br>ＰＶ&ＵＩ：匣中猫<br>主程序：The NVLmaker<br>特别感谢：热晓、闲余、三日月、614<br>==== ==== ==== ====<br>企鹅交流群：652923483",
